# Project Structure & Architecture

This is a **Paddle Billing Next.js SaaS starter kit** built with modern web technologies.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15.5.2 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript 5.9.2
- **Authentication**: Supabase (SSR-compatible)
- **Billing**: Paddle Billing (v3.2.1)
- **UI Library**: shadcn/ui with Radix UI primitives
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4.1.13
- **Package Manager**: pnpm
- **Database**: Supabase PostgreSQL

## Key Directories

### `/src/app/` - Next.js App Router
- **Pages**: [page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) files define routes
- **Layouts**: [layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) files provide shared UI
- **API Routes**: `/api/` directory for backend endpoints
- **Server Actions**: `actions.ts` files for form handling

### `/src/components/` - React Components
- **UI Components**: [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/) - shadcn/ui primitives
- **Feature Components**: Organized by domain (dashboard, home, authentication, checkout)
- **Layout Components**: Dashboard layout, headers, sidebars
- **Shared Components**: Reusable components across features

### `/src/utils/` - Utility Functions
- **Paddle Integration**: [src/utils/paddle/](mdc:src/utils/paddle/) - billing logic
- **Supabase Integration**: [src/utils/supabase/](mdc:src/utils/supabase/) - auth & database
- **Type Definitions**: [src/lib/](mdc:src/lib/) - API and database types

### `/supabase/` - Database
- **Migrations**: [supabase/migrations/](mdc:supabase/migrations/) - database schema
- **Config**: [supabase/config.toml](mdc:supabase/config.toml) - local development setup

## Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - shadcn/ui configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with `@/*` path mapping
- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration

## Architecture Patterns
- **Server Components**: Default for data fetching and static content
- **Client Components**: Marked with `'use client'` for interactivity
- **Server Actions**: For form submissions and mutations
- **Middleware**: [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts) for auth protection
- **Webhooks**: [src/app/api/webhook/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/webhook/route.ts) for Paddle events